{
  "stem": "21812.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The room had a rubber sheet on it, because they expected little kids who were still bedwetting.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I remember that vividly, because we were laughing about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they were also very, very nice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But we didn't want to be there, because, you know, the pub and the dart throwing and the noise.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So [LAUGHS] it wasn't happy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So a couple of the refugee kids, one-- one of the refugee kids, came back two day-- a day later or two days later, to the pub.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I had gotten to know him then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he said, you know, I walked up that country lane, and I knocked on the door of that-- that house at the end of the lane and asked the people to take me in, and they did.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And so I think you should do that too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, I can't believe that I did it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I think back, I say, how did I-- you know, I was 15 years old.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I barely spoke the language.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How on earth did I do it?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I don't remember by myself or I walked with another guy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I walked up that beautiful British country land.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At the end of it, there was a golf course and the moors, the-- the moors started, a beautiful spot.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I knocked on the-- I don't know whether I knocked on one door or two doors, but I knocked on the door, and also very close to that other-- a couple by the name of Hindle, H-I-N-D-L-E, had one boy about two years younger than me, or three years.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they took me in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took me in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I stayed with them for, oh, maybe five months or so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took me everywhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
